WITH YOUR FAVORITE PRESENT.

12:21.374 --> 12:23.210
ALL RIGHT, HEY,
YOU TWO BOYS GO OUT BACK

12:23.243 --> 12:28.081
AND CLEAN THE EGG YOLK
OFF THE PATIO FURNITURE,
ALL RIGHT?

12:28.115 --> 12:29.082
A DRUM.

12:29.116 --> 12:30.884
A DRUM
IS A COOL PRESENT.

12:30.918 --> 12:32.920
HEY! HEY!
HEY, EXCUSE ME.

12:32.953 --> 12:35.422
WEREN'T YOU
SUPPOSED TO BE WATCHING
YOUR BROTHERS?

12:35.455 --> 12:38.525
I WATCHED 'EM.

12:38.558 --> 12:41.394
WELL, NOT EVERY MINUTE.

12:41.428 --> 12:43.931
HOLD IT.
WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

12:43.964 --> 12:45.165
OUT WITH CHRISTINA.

12:45.198 --> 12:47.034
YOU'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE
ON A SCHOOL NIGHT.

12:47.067 --> 12:48.001
OH, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

12:48.035 --> 12:51.338
OK, THIS IS MY HOUSE,
AND THIS IS MY DAUGHTER,

12:51.371 --> 12:53.240
AND I'LL DECIDE
THOSE THINGS.

12:53.273 --> 12:55.242
LILY, GO HAVE FUN.

12:55.275 --> 12:55.976
HMM.

12:56.009 --> 12:56.743
Walt: FINE,
BUT BE BACK BY 9:00.

12:56.776 --> 12:58.511
NO, LILY,
DON'T COME BACK AT 9:00.

12:58.545 --> 13:00.080
9:30--
11:00.

13:00.113 --> 13:01.181
10:00.
MIDNIGHT.

13:01.214 --> 13:03.550
YES! THANK YOU, DAD.

13:04.584 --> 13:06.119
OH, HEY, LILY!

13:06.153 --> 13:10.257
