A STUPID WAY TO MAKE
THAT POINT,

13:20.133 --> 13:21.501
BUT THE POINT WAS VALID.

13:21.534 --> 13:23.503
SWEETIE, DO YOU HAVE
ANY QUARTERS?

13:23.536 --> 13:25.138
YEAH, BABY.

13:25.172 --> 13:27.074
HOW'S JIMMY DOING?

13:27.107 --> 13:27.774
MUCH BETTER.

13:27.807 --> 13:29.042
SO HE DOESN'T HATE ME
ANYMORE?

13:29.076 --> 13:30.343
OH, NO,
HE TOTALLY HATES YOU,

13:30.377 --> 13:33.981
BUT HE'S FORGIVEN ME
FOR MARRYING YOU.

13:34.014 --> 13:34.982
THAT'S PROGRESS.

13:35.015 --> 13:36.083
MM-HMM. THANKS.

13:36.116 --> 13:37.017
OK, IS SOMEBODY
GONNA TELL ME

13:37.050 --> 13:39.887
HOW THE OLD MAN
GOT THE PELLET IN HIS BUTT?!

13:39.920 --> 13:41.154
OK, WHOA, WHOA.
IT WAS, LIKE, 3 HOURS AGO.

13:41.188 --> 13:44.925
OK, I'M WAITING FOR LILY.
SHE'S MY DAUGHTER.

13:46.994 --> 13:48.295
HEY, BABY, YOU ARE UP LATE.

13:48.328 --> 13:51.098
OH, I JUST NEEDED
TO FIX JIMMY'S DRUM.

13:51.131 --> 13:53.300
OH, REALLY?
HE PLAYED IT?!

13:53.333 --> 13:55.135
UH, HE PLAYED WITH IT.

13:55.168 --> 13:56.569
YOU COMING UPSTAIRS?

13:56.603 --> 14:00.173
NO, I, UH, GONNA WAIT
TILL LILY GETS IN.

14:00.207 --> 14:00.941
