14:00.974 --> 14:02.309
YEAH, IT'S NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

14:02.342 --> 14:03.210
I JUST KIND OF INSISTED

14:03.243 --> 14:04.177
THAT SHE STAY OUT
ALL NIGHT.

14:04.211 --> 14:07.247
OH, NOW,
THAT'S VERY REASSURING.

14:07.280 --> 14:10.918
IT'S THAT DAMN BB GUN,
YOU KNOW?

14:10.951 --> 14:12.585
DAD REFUSES
TO TAKE IT BACK,

14:12.619 --> 14:14.454
AND JIMMY
JUST LOVES THAT THING.

14:14.487 --> 14:16.056
YEAH, TELL ME ABOUT IT.

14:16.089 --> 14:18.325
I WAS GONNA TRY
TO TAKE IT FROM HIM
THIS MORNING,

14:18.358 --> 14:22.429
AND HE JUST LOOKED UP AT ME
WITH THOSE BIG DOE EYES.

14:22.462 --> 14:26.199
NOTHING HAS EVER
MADE ME THIS HAPPY.

14:26.233 --> 14:27.600
IT IS SO HARD.

14:27.634 --> 14:29.369
LOOK, I DON'T WANT TO BE
THE KIND OF PARENT

14:29.402 --> 14:32.072
THAT SUCKS THE JOY
OUT OF HIS KID'S LIFE.

14:32.105 --> 14:33.340
YEAH, ME, NEITHER.

14:33.373 --> 14:35.976
