14:36.009 --> 14:38.145
WE'RE GOOD PARENTS,
RIGHT?

14:38.178 --> 14:40.313
HEY, WE'RE...OK.

14:40.347 --> 14:42.415
I MEAN, THERE ARE WORSE,
RIGHT?

14:42.449 --> 14:43.550
LOTS WORSE.

14:43.583 --> 14:45.585
THAT'S SOMETHING.
MM-HMM.

14:45.618 --> 14:47.220
YEAH.

14:47.254 --> 14:48.421
I'M GONNA
TAKE OUT THE TRASH.

14:48.455 --> 14:52.425
SEE? SOME PARENTS
WOULDN'T EVEN DO THAT.

14:52.459 --> 14:55.095
THEY'D LET THAT GARBAGE
PILE UP AND ROT,

14:55.128 --> 14:58.031
AND THEN THEIR KIDS
WOULD GET CHOLERA.

14:58.065 --> 14:59.166
NOT US.

14:59.199 --> 15:00.600
NOT US.

15:15.548 --> 15:18.551
GET--AAH! AAH!

15:19.652 --> 15:20.653
JIMMY?!

15:20.687 --> 15:21.354
DAD?

15:21.388 --> 15:23.256
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?!

15:23.290 --> 15:26.193
I THOUGHT THAT SOMEONE
WAS STEALING
OUR GARBAGE.

15:26.226 --> 15:28.261
I WAS JUST
DEFENDING THE HOMESTEAD.

15:28.295 --> 15:31.664
DEFENDING THE HOMESTEAD?

15:31.698 --> 15:34.267
GRANDPA SAID IT.

15:35.602 --> 15:36.970
GRANDPA--

15:37.004 --> 15:39.606
I DON'T KNOW WHY
I HAVE TO DO THIS.

15:39.639 --> 15:42.009
BECAUSE IF I DO IT,
THEN I'M THE MEAN DAD

15:42.042 --> 15:43.676
WHO'S RUINING
HIS BOY'S FUN,

15:43.710 --> 15:44.444
BUT IF YOU DO IT,

15:44.477 --> 15:45.612
THEN YOU'RE
THE MEAN GRANDFATHER,

15:45.645 --> 15:46.713
AND I CAN LIVE
WITH THAT.

15:46.746 --> 15:47.447
SO THAT'S YOUR IDEA

15:47.480 --> 15:48.681
OF TAKING CHARGE
OF YOUR FAMILY.

15:48.715 --> 15:49.749
HEY, MY FAMILY IS FINE

15:49.782 --> 15:51.451
UNTIL YOU START
MEDDLING IN IT.

15:51.484 --> 15:52.719
OH--

15:52.752 --> 15:54.021
MEN ARE SCUM!

15:54.054 --> 15:54.854
WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA.

15:54.887 --> 15:56.189
I THOUGHT YOU WENT OUT
WITH CHRISTINA.

15:56.223 --> 15:57.424
WHY ARE MEN SCUM?

15:57.457 --> 16:00.160
I JUST MEANT
IN GENERAL.

16:00.193 --> 16:02.262
OH, ANOTHER NICE
PARENTING DECISION.

16:02.295 --> 16:03.630
EVER CONSIDERED
WRITING A BOOK?

16:03.663 --> 16:05.765
HEY, LOOK, LOOK, DAD.
JUST GO UPSTAIRS

16:05.798 --> 16:07.334
AND GET THAT THING
OUT OF MY HOUSE.

16:07.367 --> 16:08.401
I'M NOT GONNA
WAKE HIM UP.

16:08.435 --> 16:09.536
OH, HE'S AWAKE, ALL RIGHT.

16:09.569 --> 16:11.438
HE'S PROTECTING
THE NEIGHBORHOOD
FROM GARBAGE THIEVES.

16:11.471 --> 16:14.007
YEAH, WELL,
IF YOU DON'T LIKE
THAT BB GUN,

16:14.041 --> 16:14.707
YOU TAKE IT AWAY.

16:14.741 --> 16:16.243
NO, NO,
YOU GAVE IT TO HIM,

16:16.276 --> 16:17.444
SO YOU TAKE IT AWAY.

16:17.477 --> 16:18.111
OH--

16:18.145 --> 16:20.013
YOU'RE TAKING AWAY
MY BB GUN?

16:20.047 --> 16:22.649
UH, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO.

16:22.682 --> 16:24.451
I'M NOT. HE IS.
NO, I'M NOT.

16:24.484 --> 16:25.318
HE IS.

16:25.352 --> 16:26.186
OH, NO, YOU DON'T.

16:26.219 --> 16:27.254
IT WAS MY GIFT
TO JIMMY.

16:27.287 --> 16:31.024
NO, NO, JIMMY, JIMMY,
GRANDPA'S DECISION
IS FINAL.

16:31.058 --> 16:31.791
I'M SORRY.

16:31.824 --> 16:33.726
