16:48.808 --> 16:50.677
YOU GOT GIRL SKIN.
NO, IT HURTS!

16:50.710 --> 16:52.112
IT DOESN'T HURT.
OH, YOU WANNA SEE

16:52.145 --> 16:53.813
HOW MUCH
IT DOESN'T HURT?
HUH?

16:53.846 --> 16:56.549
GO AHEAD. DOESN'T SCARE ME.

16:56.583 --> 16:58.785
I'M NOT GONNA
SHOOT YOU, DAD.

16:58.818 --> 17:02.222
OH, YOU'RE NOT SCARED
TO POP YOUR OLD MAN

17:02.255 --> 17:04.624
WITH THAT LITTLE
HARMLESS TOY, ARE YOU?

17:04.657 --> 17:05.658
DAD, DON'T.
HUH

17:05.692 --> 17:07.794
STOP IT, DAD, COME ON.
HUH

17:07.827 --> 17:10.097
SHOULD I KISS THE BOO-BOO!

17:10.130 --> 17:11.164
HEY!

17:11.198 --> 17:13.633
THAT'S RIGHT, WILMA.
PULL THE TRIGGER.

17:13.666 --> 17:16.503
I'M RIGHT HERE FOR YOU.

17:17.770 --> 17:18.471
I KNEW IT.

17:18.505 --> 17:21.674
I KNEW YOU
DIDN'T HAVE THE GUTS.

17:22.542 --> 17:24.444
AAH!

17:24.477 --> 17:26.679
DAD!

17:26.713 --> 17:28.081
DAD, ARE YOU OK?

17:28.115 --> 17:32.552
TELL EDDIE--

17:32.585 --> 17:33.353
YEAH?

17:33.386 --> 17:40.427
I KNOW HE'S BEEN
STEALING MY SHIRTS.

17:40.460 --> 17:41.561
SO YOU ASKED HIM
TO SHOOT YOU?

17:41.594 --> 17:46.266
THEN YOU DEMANDED
HE SHOOT YOU?

17:46.299 --> 17:47.534
THEN HE SHOT YOU?

17:47.567 --> 17:49.269
RIGHT IN THE CAN.

17:49.302 --> 17:50.237
NOW, ARREST HIM.

17:50.270 --> 17:51.771
ALL RIGHT.
WHAT?!

17:51.804 --> 17:53.540
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
GO DOWN TO THE STATION
WITH ME.

17:53.573 --> 17:56.409
WAIT,
YOU WOULD ARREST HIM
FOR A BB WOUND?

17:56.443 --> 17:58.811
IF YOU WANT TO FILE
AN ASSAULT CHARGE,
I HAVE TO.

17:58.845 --> 18:03.216
YOU STAY OUT
OF MY FAMILY'S BUSINESS.

18:03.250 --> 18:05.318
BUT YOU
JUST WANTED ME TO--

18:05.352 --> 18:07.820
MOVE ALONG!

18:08.721 --> 18:10.690
HEY, THANKS, DAD.

18:10.723 --> 18:13.260
ARRESTING MY LITTLE BOY.

18:14.294 --> 18:15.795
DAD,
I'M SORRY I SHOT YOU.

18:15.828 --> 18:19.132
WELL,
MAYBE I ASKED FOR IT.

18:19.166 --> 18:20.433
YOU DID ASK FOR IT.

18:20.467 --> 18:23.470
DAD, BUT YOU GOT
TO LET ME BE BOSS
IN MY OWN HOUSE.

18:23.503 --> 18:26.173
I MEAN,
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING,
GETTING THAT BB GUN?

18:26.206 --> 18:28.341
YOU WANNA KNOW THE TRUTH?

18:28.375 --> 18:29.542
I WAS PANICKED.

18:29.576 --> 18:33.880
EVERY DAMN TOY I LOOKED AT
HAD ONE OF THOSE
POKÃ‰MEN ON IT.

18:33.913 --> 18:36.449
OR THOSE IDIOTIC ROBOTS

18:36.483 --> 18:39.752
THAT DON'T KNOW IF THEY'RE
TRUCKS OR DINOSAURS.

18:40.720 --> 18:42.389
I WAS CONFUSED.

18:42.422 --> 18:43.523
IT USED TO BE SIMPLE.

18:43.556 --> 18:47.560
I JUST WANTED A TOY
ME AND JIMMY COULD ENJOY
TOGETHER.

18:47.594 --> 18:49.529
Nurse: MR. FINNERTY?

18:50.230 --> 18:52.732
DAD--DAD, YOU COULD HAVE
JUST ASKED ME.

18:52.765 --> 18:55.502
OH, YEAH.
YOU GOT HIM A DRUM.

18:55.535 --> 18:57.837
OK. ENJOY YOUR SURGERY.

18:57.870 --> 19:01.208
HE'S GOING TO
ADULT CIRCUMCISION.

19:02.642 --> 19:04.744
Lily:
I MEAN, COME ON.

19:04.777 --> 19:06.846
CHRISTINA
IS A FLAG GIRL.

19:06.879 --> 19:10.350
A FLAG GIRL IS
JUST A FAT CHEERLEADER.

19:10.383 --> 19:11.784
NOW--NOW,
DON'T GET ME WRONG.

19:11.818 --> 19:15.655
SHE'S MY BEST FRIEND,
BUT WHAT IS WITH
ALL THE GLITTER?

19:15.688 --> 19:17.724
IT'S, LIKE, GLITTER
EVERYWHERE ON HER.

19:17.757 --> 19:20.227
IS SHE--
IS SHE A PERSON,

19:20.260 --> 19:23.263
OR IS SHE A DISCO BALL?

19:23.296 --> 19:25.265
WHO'S CHRISTINA?
THE REAL TALL ONE?

19:25.298 --> 19:26.566
