WITH THE GLITTER.

19:26.599 --> 19:29.436
OH, OH! THE BRUNETTE.
OH, PLEASE.

19:29.469 --> 19:31.638
SHE'S NOTHING.

19:31.671 --> 19:32.505
REALLY?

19:32.539 --> 19:34.507
YEAH, I'VE KNOWN
LOTS OF GIRLS LIKE HER.

19:34.541 --> 19:36.209
YOU KNOW WHAT SHE'S
GOT GOING FOR HER?

19:36.243 --> 19:37.844
