SHE'S SLUTTY?

19:40.880 --> 19:43.583
NO, I'M SAYING
SHE'S OBVIOUS...

19:43.616 --> 19:45.652
NOT COMPLICATED.

19:45.685 --> 19:48.788
OK,
AND SHE'S GOT NO DEPTH.

19:48.821 --> 19:51.758
YOU KNOW,
GUYS AREN'T THREATENED
BY HER.

19:51.791 --> 19:53.393
SO, I'M COMPLICATED?

19:53.426 --> 19:56.563
YEAH. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU.
YOU'RE...

