20:00.300 --> 20:01.801
DO I SCARE YOU?

20:01.834 --> 20:03.670
YOU SCARE THE CRAP
OUT OF ME.

20:03.703 --> 20:05.772
THAT'S COOL.

20:05.805 --> 20:06.806
YEAH.

20:06.839 --> 20:07.507
HMM.

20:07.540 --> 20:12.612
SO, UH,
YOU DON'T LIKE SLUTTY?

20:17.617 --> 20:19.386
NO.

20:21.020 --> 20:23.423
I DON'T WANT TO BE
THE MEAN DAD.

20:23.456 --> 20:25.292
MY DAD IS THE MEAN DAD.

20:25.325 --> 20:29.729
LOOK, SEAN, EVERY DAD
HAS TO BE THE MEAN DAD.

20:29.762 --> 20:31.964
IT'S WHY BEING THE MOM
IS SO GREAT.

20:31.998 --> 20:34.534
