IS THAT YOU HATE ME.

20:52.719 --> 20:54.287
YEAH.

20:55.021 --> 20:57.557
WELL, IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN DO TO GET YOU TO LIKE ME?

20:57.590 --> 21:00.893
EXCEPT GIVE YOU BACK
THAT BB GUN?

21:00.927 --> 21:01.761
NO.

21:01.794 --> 21:02.595
HEY, LOOK, JIMMY,

21:02.629 --> 21:04.364
I DIDN'T WANT TO BE
THE BAD GUY HERE,

21:04.397 --> 21:05.398
OK, BUT SOMETIMES AS A DAD

21:05.432 --> 21:08.535
YOU GOT TO MAKE DECISIONS
THAT AREN'T TOO POPULAR,

21:08.568 --> 21:10.803
AND I DIDN'T WANT
TO HAVE TO TAKE THAT GUN AWAY,

21:10.837 --> 21:11.671
BUT IT WAS DANGEROUS.

21:11.704 --> 21:14.507
YEAH, I KNOW.
YOU SHOT GRANDPA
WITH IT.

21:14.541 --> 21:17.344
YES, I DID.

21:17.377 --> 21:19.011
BUT THAT'S NOT THE POINT.

21:19.045 --> 21:21.914
THE POINT IS, AS A DAD,

21:21.948 --> 21:23.816
YOU KNOW, I HAVE TO DO
WHAT I THINK IS RIGHT,

21:23.850 --> 21:28.788
AND YOU ARE JUST
GONNA HAVE TO LEARN
TO UNDERSTAND THAT.

21:32.692 --> 21:33.860
DAD...

21:33.893 --> 21:34.694
YEAH?

21:34.727 --> 21:35.762
I DON'T HATE YOU.

21:35.795 --> 21:37.664
I'M GLAD TO HEAR THAT.

21:37.697 --> 21:40.066
NOW CAN I HAVE
MY BB GUN BACK?

21:41.067 --> 21:41.901
NO.

21:41.934 --> 21:42.835
I HATE YOU!

21:42.869 --> 21:44.036
NO, YOU DON'T.
YOU ALREADY SAID
YOU DIDN'T.

21:44.070 --> 21:45.572
NO, BUT I DO.
TOO LATE.

21:45.605 --> 21:46.506
CAN I HAVE A REAL GUN?

21:46.539 --> 21:48.508
NOPE.
OK, THEN
JUST A BB GUN.

21:48.541 --> 21:49.409
UH, NO.

21:49.442 --> 21:50.109
OH, I HATE YOU.

21:50.142 --> 21:51.578
NO, YOU DON'T.
I DO.

21:51.611 --> 21:52.512
YOU CAN'T
TAKE IT BACK.

21:52.545 --> 21:54.013
I WON'T SHOOT
ANY MORE FRUIT.

21:54.046 --> 21:54.847
YOU LOVE ME.

22:05.024 --> 22:08.528
CAN'T TAKE THAT THING
AWAY FROM HIM, CAN WE?

22:08.561 --> 22:11.398
NOPE.
